Returns <code>NOT_FOUND</code> if the topic does not exist. After a topic is deleted, a new topic may be created with the same name; this is an entirely new topic with none of the old configuration or subscriptions. All messages retained in the subscription are immediately dropped. Calls to <code>Pull</code> after deletion will return <code>NOT_FOUND</code>.
